      <title>DOJ fires officials who investigated Trump. And, what to know about DeepSeek</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/01/28/g-s1-45039/up-first-newsletter-justice-department-firings-stock-market-deepseek-ai</link>
