 - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x928+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F78%2F40%2F61e273744c35b5d34941c6984e3e%2Ffamily-lny-dinner.jpeg" class="img" alt="Penny Lee and her family gather for a Lunar New Year feast." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Penny Lee and her family gather for a Lunar New Year feast.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Credit Penny Lee                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Several readers said they clean their homes top to bottom on the days leading up to the new year.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;"You want to do that before the new year itself to get rid of any bad luck that came with the past year and make way for good fortune and prosperity into the new year," said Chelsea Tan, a baker from Reston, Va.&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;p&gt;Penny Lee of Silver Spring, Md., has a thorough cleaning routine. She declutters her closets, donates clothes she no longer needs, disposes of expired food from her fridge and pantry and reorganizes all the spaces in her home.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Many readers cautioned that you should stop cleaning once the new year arrives. "Throwing anything out on the new year means throwing out your good luck," Tran Tran of Worcester, Mass., said.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-44570" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 960;         --source-height: 830;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/960x830+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1a%2F10%2Fe72aedc64a2895fc34bc44f568bd%2Ftrantran-worcester-ma-picture.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/960x830+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1a%2F10%2Fe72aedc64a2895fc34bc44f568bd%2Ftrantran-worcester-ma-picture.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/960x830+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1a%2F10%2Fe72aedc64a2895fc34bc44f568bd%2Ftrantran-worcester-ma-picture.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/960x830+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1a%2F10%2Fe72aedc64a2895fc34bc44f568bd%2Ftrantran-worcester-ma-picture.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/960x830+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1a%2F10%2Fe72aedc64a2895fc34bc44f568bd%2Ftrantran-worcester-ma-picture.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/960x830+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1a%2F10%2Fe72aedc64a2895fc34bc44f568bd%2Ftrantran-worcester-ma-picture.jpg 1600w, https://npr.br