      <title>What to know for Trump's inauguration. And, a Civil Rights icon remembers MLK Jr.</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/01/20/g-s1-43670/up-first-newsletter-donald-trump-inauguration-day-martin-luther-king-jr-day-tiktok</link>
